title: HOUR 1- Mike Florio and Ross Tucker Oct 23, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Mike Florio and Ross Tucker Oct 23, 2020
description:
Mike Florio tells Dan that Daniel Jones has no awareness in the pocket or while he was running in wide open field. Mike says the Giants will need to look at new QB possibilities. Ross Tucker says that the Daniel Jones fall was the funniest thing he has ever seen on a football field.
